Lacoste created a custom walk-on jacket for Novak Djokovic at Roland Garros, and the detail that makes it special is the orange clay from the courts worked directly into the piece.
Not inspired by the clay. Not the color of clay. Actual Roland Garros clay. ItвҖҷs the kind of thing youвҖҷd only notice if someone told you, and now you canвҖҷt unsee it. What do you think of fashion meeting the court like this?
